{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop criminalising kids - raise the age of criminal responsibility to 18",
        "additional_details": "We think the criminalisation of children as young as 10 is a stain on our national life.\r\n \r\nWe think young children going to court, imprisoning them in Young Offenders institutions, sentencing them for along time for childhood acts, and naming and shaming in the media is wrong.\r\n \r\nWe feel children with criminal records are scarred for life.\r\n \r\nYou cannot vote until 18 so we think you should not be subject to criminal law until the same age.\r\n \r\nEducate. Understand. Treat. Support. Release.",
        "background": "Raise the age of criminal responsibility to 18, to match the age when we can vote in elections.",
